<div id="review_3393712285" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3393712285" />
    <a title="Chris" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1041790-chris"><img alt="Chris" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1222203410p2/1041790.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3393712285?book_show_action=true">Jun 15, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Chris" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Chris" href="/user/show/1041790-chris">Chris</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3393712285" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18362002457113906925">The author has used a Shakespearean tragedy and WW Jacobs&apos; &quot;Monkey&apos;s Paw&quot; as his inspiration. Bad things happen, but when something good occurs, there is a cost.</span>
  <span id="freeText18362002457113906925" style="display:none">The author has used a Shakespearean tragedy and WW Jacobs' "Monkey's Paw" as his inspiration. Bad things happen, but when something good occurs, there is a cost.</span>
  <a data-text-id="18362002457113906925" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

