</a><a href="mailto:duncan@duncanmhamilton.com" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1545230739i/26772271.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
